Name: Average time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Total time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Checklist Completed across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes Manuscript Export Succeeded to be followed by SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time for Manuscript Export Succeeded to occur after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total resolution time of Manuscript Export Succeeded in cases that eventually reach SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants where reviewer assignment succeeds on the first attempt
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in high-complexity variants (those with more than three reviewer-related activities)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Minimum time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in accepted manuscripts
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Elapsed time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation in resubmission pathways
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed to occur after Manuscript Export Succeeded in variants without reviewer reminders
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in cases involving Assign a Different Editor
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation in accepted revision cycles
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Cycle Time of Manuscript Export Succeeded measured from its occurrence to the next Manuscript Export Succeeded in multi-export cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit in rejection-with-resubmit pathways
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'average'}"
